icant for\nquantum information scrambling, our results also advance understating of\ndecoherence in processes involving backward time evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Mar 2019 16:28:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 Mar 2019 08:31:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 15 Apr 2019 12:26:02 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 23 May 2019 14:00:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-11"}
