graph. For every case I examine I\nfind a similar or better performance from the domain wall encoding as compared\nto one hot, but this advantage is highly dependent on the structure of the\nproblem. For encoding some problems, I find an advantage similar to the one\nfound by embedding in a Pegasus graph compared to embedding in a chimera graph.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Mar 2019 17:21:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 16 Apr 2019 17:02:01 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 21 Jun 2019 14:23:21 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Sat, 20 Jul 2019 14:52:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-07"}
