 proof of a theorem of Helton and Spitkovsky, generalizing their result in\nthe process.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Mar 2019 20:07:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 8 Jul 2019 20:13:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-10"}
